snippet.title: Clarity: Connecting With Your Purpose - The Mindset Mentor with Tania Kolar   and guest Amber Price
snippet.description:
In this episode, Tania speaks with The Clarity Expert and Psychic Medium, Amber Price. They discuss how to get clear and discover your purpose. They discuss chakras, blocks, and how to tap into your intuition to live your best life. They also discuss the different soul archetypes and how to determine which archetype you resonate with, and more.

The Mindset Mentor, as heard on Sauga 960 AM talk radio- May 11, 2021. 

Host: Tania Kolar 
Guest: Amber Price
